nodes.text: Devish was a male Human lieutenant of the Sith Empire living during the Cold War.

Lieutenant Devish appears in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic under npc.location.open_worlds.class.sith_sorcerer.chapter_1.preparations directory. He does not appear during Sith Inquisitor Chapter 1 mission "Preparations" in the live game.
